<emphasis id="F2B0EAC9FFACFFC30E93BA91C069FA33" bold="true" box="[431,556,1408,1432]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="288">Amydetes</emphasis>
Illiger, 1807
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="58FF2A5EFFACFFC30DDFBA6EC12EFA32" box="[739,875,1407,1433]" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="12.[160,225,1378,1401]" captionTargetBox="[164,1144,144,1340]" captionTargetId="figure-42@12.[163,1152,142,1346]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="Figure 3. Diversity of fireflies of the Serra dos Órgãos, including Amydetinae, Psilocladinae, Lampyrinae, and Incertae sedis taxa. A – Amydetes fastigiata, B – Magnoculus obscurus, C – Cladodes pauper, D – Cladodes illigeri, E – Cladodes stellata, F – Vesta thoracica, G – Araucariocladus hiems (modified from Silveira and Mermudes 2017), H – Psilocladus grandis, I – Psilocladus sigillatus, J – Psilocladus pulcher, K – Scissicauda disjuncta (modified from Silveira et al. 2016a), L – Ethra axillaris, M – Ethra marginata, N – Ethra addita, O – Ethra inculta. Scale bar: 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5021074" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5021074/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="288">Figure 3 A</figureCitation>
)
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
